About NCC

Based in Ratnanagar‑4, Chitwan, New Capital College offers science and computer labs, hotel‑management practice space, library and seminar hall.

Modern Labs

Hands‑on spaces for Science, Computing and HM.

Library

Light, quiet and well‑stocked for deep study.

Hostel

Comfortable, supervised living close to class.

Programs

We offer +2 in Science,Hotel Management and Management, and BBS at undergraduate level.

+2 Science

Physics, Chemistry with optional Biology, Maths, Computer Science.

+2 Management

Business basics with Accountancy, Economics, Computer Science, Maths,Social Studies and Lifeskill Education.

BBS (TU)

Managerial thinking and communication for business careers.

Student Support

  • Assessments & feedback
  • Extra classes & counselling
  • Entrance preparation and Bridge Course for SEE appeared students.
  • Internships & industry visits

Vision

Build good study habits, hold high expectations and discover your own voice.

Mission

Provide accessible, high‑quality learning opportunities that lead to recognized skills and real‑world readiness.
